dialog.body: Hello! Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is James Hall. May I have your name, please?
Hi, my name is Lori Hill.
Nice to meet you, Lori. Could you please provide me with your policy number?
Sure, it's one two three four five.
Thank you. Can you confirm your date of birth for verification purposes?
Yes, it's zero four dash zero seven dash one nine eight zero.
Great, thank you for confirming. Is there anything specific you need assistance with today?
I'd like to add a new vehicle to my policy.
Certainly, I can assist you with that. Let's get the details of the new vehicle. Can you provide me with the make, model, and year?
Thank you for your time, Lori. If you need any further assistance, feel free to reach out. Have a wonderful day!
